Kinder has decided to recall a selection of European labelled Kinder products as they may contain salmonella. They were manufactured at the Arlon factory in Belgium. Some products, which were intended for the European market only and have already been recalled in Europe, have been imported into the UK by UK importers not linked to Ferrero. Pack size: 133g Best before: August 21, 2022 Pack size: 100g Best before: August 21, 2022 Pack size: 193g Best before: August 21, 2022 Pack size: 132g Best before: August 21, 2022 Pack size: 100g Best before: August 21, 2022 Pack size: 100g Best before: August 20, 2022 Pack size: 100g Best before: April 20, 2022 Pack size: 125g and 200g Best before: October 26, 2022 Pack size: 242g Best before: August 21, 2022 Pack size: All Best before: August 21, 2022 Pack size: 100g Best before: August 21, 2022 Pack size: 133g Best before: August 21, 2022. READ MORE: The Food Standards Agency (FSA) issued a risk statement to warn consumers. "The possible presence of Salmonella in the products listed above. "Symptoms caused by Salmonella usually include fever, diarrhoea and abdominal cramps." The FSA provided a warning for any customers who may have purchased the above products. DON'T MISS They stated: "If you have bought the above products do not eat them. "Instead, please take them back to the store where you purchased the products and request a refund." Additionally, they explained the actions taken by Kinder to ensure the safety of its customers. "Ferrero is recalling the above products. "Point of sale notices will be displayed in retail stores that are selling these products. "These notices explain to customers why the products are being recalled and tell them what to do if they have bought the products." The FSA advised that this most recent recall does not replace earlier versions. In April 2022, Kinder recalled a selection of confectionary products over fears that they may be contaminated with salmonella. Pack size: 20g Best before: All dates up to and including January 4, 2023 Pack size: 20g x 3 pack Best before: All dates up to and including January 4, 2023 Pack size: 100g Best before: All dates up to and including August 21, 2022 Pack size: 75g Best before: All dates up to and including August 21, 2022 Pack size: 150g Best before: All dates up to and including August 21, 2022 Pack size: 70g, 200g and 320g Best before: All dates up to and including January 4, 2023.